| The Completely Fair Scheduler                                      |
|   from the i'm-always-late dept.                                   |
|   posted by CmdrTaco on Sunday April 22, @11:31 (Linux)            |
|   http://linux.slashdot.org/article.pl?sid=07/04/22/1335255        |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

hichetu writes "Kernel trap has a nice summary of what is going on behind
the scenes to [0]change the Linux Scheduler. The O(1) Linux scheduler is
going to be changed so that it is fair to interactive tasks. You will be
surprised to know that O(1) is really too good not to have any
side-effects on fairness to all tasks."

